name: fastq
query: SELECT cancer_path, human_sex FROM human JOIN cancer ON human.human_id = cancer.human_id;

name: fastq_man
query: SELECT cancer_path FROM human JOIN cancer ON human.human_id = cancer.human_id WHERE human.human_sex = 'man';

name: fastq_?
query: SELECT ? FROM human JOIN cancer ON human.human_id = cancer.human_id WHERE human.human_sex = '?';
